title: Cafe Minou
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian-friendly cafe inside Chautauqua Natural Foods market. Offers soups, salads, rice crust pizza, quiche, sushi, wraps, baked goods, fresh juices, smoothies, and more. There is an outdoor picnic table across the street.
